            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">28 May [1858] ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ In reply to the enquiry made in your letter of the 22nd instant, ¶  I have the honor to inform you that the only holidays allowed to daily laborers of this Department are Chr...</supplied>
